{{PIE root|en|bʰewgʰ}}
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|boga|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*bugô}}. Cognate with West Frisian {{term|boge|lang=fy}}, Dutch {{term|boog|lang=nl}}, German {{term|Bogen|lang=de}}, Danish {{term|bue|lang=da}}, Swedish {{term|båge|lang=sv}}.

